#, no-c-format
msgid "Both commands will output their completion time once they have finished."
msgstr "Les deux commandes indiqueront leur durée d'exécution dès qu'elles auront terminé."

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simultaneously with the two running <command>dd</command> threads, you can "
"monitor the performance in real time by using the "
"<application>iotop</application> utility. To install the "
